1
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,200
Savior

2
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:52,360
Savior

3
00:00:52,600 --> 00:00:54,280
Why didn't you tell me before you came?

4
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,400
So I could make arrangements.

5
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,040
Hei Yanluo

6
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:00,080
How the hell did you train your men?

7
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:04,200
You blind idiots.

8
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,360
He was once my Savior.

9
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,480
Without Brother Wu Di,

10
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,720
I'd be crippled by now.

11
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:11,160
You dare disrespect my Savior?

12
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,320
I'll fucking kill you.

13
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:13,440
Enough.

14
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:14,720
Hei Yanluo

15
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,720
We're in a hurry.

16
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,760
Re-check the cargo.

17
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:18,360
No need.

18
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:19,360
Let them through.

19
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:19,680
But...

20
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,240
Boss.

21
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,560
If we don't re-check it,

22
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,360
they've got cameras up there.

23
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,760
It'll be hard to explain upstairs.

24
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,640
I won't make it hard on you.

25
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:26,840
Then check it.

26
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:27,440
Okay.

27
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:28,480
I'll do it myself.

28
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:37,640
Boss.

29
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,680
We found a batch of weapons.

30
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,360
These are the real deal.

31
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,960
You call these weapons?

32
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:46,440
Are you blind?

33
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,680
These are toy guns.

34
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,320
Can't you tell?

35
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,400
How are toy guns smuggling?

36
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,120
Light and sound toy guns.

37
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:01,760
Yeah.

38
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,680
Light and sound toy guns.

39
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,640
They're pretty well-made.

40
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,840
Just like the real thing.

41
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,360
Put them back.

42
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,800
Let them through.

43
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,160
Let them through!

44
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,360
Boss.

45
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,600
We're just letting them go?

46
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,160
Like hell we are.

47
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,240
That Zhao Wu Di's bad news.

48
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,240
He's the one who let us go.

49
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,840
Aren't you here to play Brother Wu Di?

50
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,160
How'd you know about Hei Yanluo?

51
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,480
Someone mysterious told me.

52
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:29,960
You're getting more like Brother Wu Di.

53
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,280
Means I'm playing the part well.

54
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:48,880
Hong Ye

55
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:56,880
Sit.

56
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,160
Hong Ye.

57
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,600
This result...

58
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,680
are you satisfied with it?

59
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,280
Satisfied.

60
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,840
I've got a question.

61
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,640
How'd you get Hei Yanluo

62
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,120
to show you that much respect?

63
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:17,960
Hong Ye,

64
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,240
didn't we agree already?

65
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,240
You pick the time and place.

66
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,560
As for how we move the goods,

67
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,040
that's my call.

68
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:27,960
Can't you understand what I'm asking?

69
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:35,760
How do you never learn?

70
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,560
Hong Ye...

71
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,440
This money,

72
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,120
consider it my investment in you.

73
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,960
Starting today,

74
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,080
we're

75
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,480
family.

76
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,320
I didn't expect

77
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,480
you'd pull a bait-and-switch

78
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:14,240
to fool that old fox, Hong Ye.

79
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,560
Don't celebrate too soon.

80
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,640
A guy like Hong Ye

81
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,120
isn't that easy to fool.

82
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:23,120
And he knows

83
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,320
how important Dr. Zhang is to you.

84
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,200
He won't let him go that easily.

85
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:29,480
Then what's your plan?

86
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,520
My plan is...

87
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,520
never put all our eggs

88
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,200
in one basket.

89
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,280
In Dongba,

90
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,280
the only one who can check Hong Ye

91
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,520
is Sister Fei.

92
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,240
Since Sister Fei knows about this,

93
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,400
we bring her in.

94
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:45,840
Let her stir things up.

95
00:04:46,640 --> 00:04:47,960
That's the only way we're safe.

96
00:04:49,320 --> 00:04:51,840
But we just cut a deal with Hong Ye.

97
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:54,240
And now we turn to Sister Fei?

98
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,680
If Hong Ye finds out,

99
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,680
won't he blow up?

100
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,920
We're the distributors right now.

101
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:03,120
Nobody can replace us.

102
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,960
So even if we play both sides,

103
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:07,320
they'll turn a blind eye.

104
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,320
Remember.

105
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,880
That's the survival rule in Dongba.

106
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,400
Tell me.

107
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,680
How do you wanna work with me?

108
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,440
Sister Fei,

109
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,920
I'm a married man now.

110
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,400
Today,

111
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:44,280
you can be Shen Xingyu's husband.

112
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,640
Someday,

113
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:50,360
you'll be my man.

114
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,480
Sister Fei,

115
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,840
I'm really here to talk business.

116
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,360
Why talk business?

117
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:08,360
Be my little man.

118
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:10,480
My business

119
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,400
will all be yours.

120
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,440
Sister Fei,

121
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,520
stop teasing me.

122
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:20,280
Don't test me with your new identity.

123
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:23,400
So?

124
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,160
How do you wanna work with me?

125
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,120
Ah Kun called.

126
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:32,400
Said that bitch Feifei

127
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,640
looks like she wants to steal our business.

128
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,680
She's getting more and more arrogant.

129
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,440
I should've wiped her out last time.

130
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,760
No rush.

131
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,680
There's plenty of business to go around.

132
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,200
The pie's big enough.

133
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:47,400
We can all have a slice.

134
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,960
But on one condition.

135
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,760
She doesn't get in our way.

136
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:52,440
Uncle,

137
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:53,800
what's she doing?

138
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,840
She's forcing our hand.

139
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,720
You think we'll let her lead us by the nose?

140
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,360
Idiot.

141
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,120
Use your damn head.

142
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,760
People with desires are easy to control.

143
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,920
But people who want nothing?

144
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,800
Keeping them around is pointless.

145
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,440
Listen up, kid.

146
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,440
You really can't touch her.

147
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:14,600
I need to see how she reacts.

148
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,680
Got it?

149
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,480
Got it.

150
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,640
I know you pulled me into this

151
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:27,600
to keep Hong Ye's power in check.

152
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,520
But for you,

153
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,040
I can do it.

154
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,520
Thanks, Sister Fei.

155
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,680
This drink,

156
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:35,840
I'll down it.

157
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,480
If you need anything later,

158
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:40,960
I'm at your service.

159
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:43,280
Yeah?

160
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,920
Then I'm not feeling so good right now.

161
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,240
Give me a little massage.

162
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:55,520
What?

163
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,840
I've helped you so much,

164
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,920
and you won't even do this little favor?

165
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,480
Why aren't you picking up?

166
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,440
Did something happen?

167
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:16,040
President Xingyu,

168
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,480
Brother Wu Di is so capable.

169
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,920
He'll be fine, don't worry.

170
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,120
But he's not Zhao Wu Di, after all.

171
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:21,720
No.

172
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,760
I have to go check.

173
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,080
I'm coming with you.

174
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,240
Keep calling him.

175
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,280
Tell me the second you reach him.

176
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,480
Be careful, President Xingyu.

177
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:39,440
What,

178
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,040
you don't want to?

179
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,280
Adi!

180
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,120
Save me!

181
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,080
Save me!

182
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,120
Wanna save Shen Xingyu?

183
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,560
Where are you?

184
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,960
If you wanna save her,

185
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,200
check the location.

186
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:48,520
Boss,

187
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:50,040
Like you ordered,

188
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,440
we faked Dawa's voice.

189
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,640
We're pros at phone scams.

190
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:55,040
It'll sound exactly like him.

191
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:55,800
Wrong.

192
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,200
He won't trust just a voice.

193
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,480
What he'll trust

194
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:01,400
is the signal he tracks himself.

195
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,840
Then it's even easier.

196
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,520
I tied

197
00:10:04,280 --> 00:10:05,800
Shen Xingyu's SIM card

198
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:07,120
to a rabbit

199
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,440
and tossed it into the Death Jungle.

200
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:10,320
Make sure he really goes in.

201
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,120
Don't worry.

202
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,520
I've got the guys watching right here.

203
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,360
The moment he goes in,

204
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,320
they'll tip us off right away.

205
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:15,720
Bring Shen Xingyu over.

206
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:18,320
Bring Shen Xingyu in.

207
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,320
Sit.

208
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:30,280
Let's keep it short today.

209
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,240
I know Adi isn't Zhao Wu Di.

210
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,240
And I also know

211
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,760
why you came to Dongba

212
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:38,840
was to find who killed your husband.

213
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:41,280
Adi told you that?

214
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:47,560
This is the hitman's file.

215
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:50,200
After he took the job to kill Zhao Wu Di,

216
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,520
he left Dongba

217
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,720
and never showed up again.

218
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:55,480
Recently, someone spotted him in Country F.

219
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,680
You can go look for him.

220
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,120
Why are you helping me?

221
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,400
I'm not helping you.

222
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,880
I'm helping myself.

223
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,200
Ever since you came to Dongba,

224
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,280
you've thrown everything out of balance.

225
00:11:07,280 --> 00:11:09,320
Hong Ye's people haven't been back since.

226
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,640
My business has tanked.

227
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,840
What's that got to do with me?

228
00:11:23,560 --> 00:11:24,640
Shen Xingyu,

229
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,880
As far as I'm concerned,

230
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,640
you're a jinx.

231
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,720
I've wanted you gone for a long time.

232
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,760
I know you've got someone backing you.

233
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,360
So I'm giving you a chance.

234
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,880
Get out of Dongba, now.

235
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,120
Where's Adi?

236
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,080
Where is he?

237
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,280
How would I know?

238
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,240
In that case,

239
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,560
we've got nothing else to talk about.

240
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,280
Give me the phone.

241
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:08,440
Xingyu!

242
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:10,640
Xingyu!

243
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:12,480
Xingyu!

244
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,760
Xingyu!
